  is-segalГ—is-rezk-completeвҶҗis-complete-segal = Г—-is-localвҶҗis-local-вЁ„вӮҒб¶ 

  is-complete-segalвҶҗis-segalвҶҗis-rezk-complete
    : is-segal A вҶ’ is-rezk-complete A вҶ’ is-complete-segal A
  is-complete-segalвҶҗis-segalвҶҗis-rezk-complete = is-local-вЁ„вӮҒб¶ вҶҗis-local
